20won%20their%20next%20six%20games%20by%20great%20margins%20and%20knocked%20out%20defending%20champions%20Chennai%20Super%20Kings%20(CSK)%20in%20a%20virtual%20knockout%20clash%20to%20secure%20the%20final%20playoff%20spot%20on%20basis%20of%20net-run-rate.%20However%2C%20the%2017-year-old%20long%20wait%20for%20the%20trophy%20continues%20after%20the%20loss%20to%20RR.%20Nonetheless%2C%20the%20team's%20performance%20this%20season%20has%20won%20them%20a%20lot%20of%20acclaim%20from%20fans%2C%20experts%20and%20players%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20video%20posted%20by%20RCB's%20official%20X%20handle%2C%20Virat%20said%20that%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20season%20was%20an%20under-par%20performance%20from%20the%20franchise%20and%20they%20were%20not%20able%20to%20live%20up%20to%20their%20standards%20as%20cricketers.%20But%20he%20will%20cherish%20and%20remember%20the%20way%20his%20team%20bounced%20back%20from%20adversity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20be%20really%20honest%2C%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20season%20was%20a%20really%20under-par%20performance%20from%20us.%20The%20standards%20that%20we%20have%20as%20cricketers%2C%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20live%20up%20to%20them.%20Then%20we%20started%20expressing%20ourselves%2C%20played%20for%20our%20own%20self-respect.%20Our%20confidence%20came%20back.%20The%20way%20turned%20things%20around%20and%20qualified%20was%20truly%20special.%20It%20is%20something%20I%20will%20cherish%20and%20remember%2C%20because%20it%20took%20a%20lot%20of%20character%20and%20heart%20from%20the%20boys%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-media-max-width%3D%5C%22560%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUnfortunately%2C%20sport%20is%20not%20a%20fairytale%20and%20our%20remarkable%20run%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FIPL2024%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23IPL2024%3C%2Fa%3E%20came%20to%20an%20end.%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20Faf%20du%20Plessis%20and%20Dinesh%20Karthik%20express%20their%20emotions%20and%20thank%20fans%20for%20their%20unwavering%20support.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FPlayBold%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23PlayBold%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2F%25E0%25B2%25A8%25E0%25B2%25AE%25E0%25B3%258D%25E0%25B2%25AERCB%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23%E0%B2%A8%E0%B2%AE%E0%B3%8D%E0%B2%AERCB%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FFYygVD3UiC%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FFYygVD3UiC%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20(%40RCBTweets)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRCBTweets%2Fstatus%2F1793492930872959167%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2023%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20thanked%20the%20fans%20for%20supporting%20the%20team%20and%20turning%20up%20in%20huge%20numbers%20all%20over%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESkipper%20Faf%20said%20that%20the%20last%20six%20games%20were%20special%20for%20the%20way%20RCB%20turned%20things%20around%20but%20in%20the%20eliminator%2C%20they%20fell%20short%20by%20around%2015%20runs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20innings%20was%20tricky%2C%20the%20ball%20was%20moving%20around%20and%20it%20was%20a%20bit%20slow%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EReflecting%20on%20the%20fan's%20support%20even%20though%20the%20team%20was%20down%20and%20out%20halfway%20through%20the%20season%2C%20Faf%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20down%20halfway%20through%20the%20season.%20But%20still%20the%20fans%2C%20every%20match%2C%20every%20stadium.%20We%20could%20hear%20the%20chants.%20Once%20we%20got%20that%20momentum%2C%20we%20ran%20with%20it.%20We%20are%20extremely%20grateful%20for%20it.%20Sad%20we%20cannot%20reach%20the%20finals.%20But%20from%20where%20we%20were%20and%20where%20we%20finished%2C%20I%20am%20really%20proud%20of%20the%20boys.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESummarising%20the%20team's%20season%2C%20Dinesh%2C%20who%20is%20likely%20playing%20his%20last-ever%20IPL%20season%2C%20said%20that%20the%20team%20felt%20that%20this%20could%20very%20well%20be%20the%20year%20when%20they%20lift%20the%20trophy%20because%20of%20the%20way%20they%20turned%20things%20around%2C%20but%20the%20%26quot%3Bhard%20day%26quot%3B%20that%20loomed%20over%20their%20heads%20happened%20to%20be%20the%20eliminator.%20He%20also%20said%20that%20dew%20came%20in%20the%20second%20innings%20and%20it%20became%20easy%20to%20bat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20sports%2C%20there%20is%20no%20fairytale%20ending.%20There%20is%20always%20a%20hard%20day%20when%20things%20do%20not%20go%20your%20way.%20It%20was%20that%20day.%20As%20it%20is%20in%20the%20evening%20games%2C%20dew%20came%20and%20it%20became%20easy%20to%20bat%20on.%20But%20still%2C%20we%20should%20be%20proud%20of%20the%20fight%20we%20put%20up.%20That%20is%20all%20we%20can%20ask%20for.%20Attitude%20matters.%20The%20belief%20in%20wanting%20to%20do%20something%20special%20matters.%20On%20both%20counts%2C%20RCB%20had%20a%20really%20special%20season.%20A%20season%20where%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20will%20look%20at%20and%20say%20'Wow%2C%20good%20effort'.%20We%20are%20proud%20of%20ourselves%20and%20I%20also%20hope%20fans%20are%20also%20proud%20of%20us%20for%20what%20we%20have%20done%20this%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Dinesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EComing%20to%20the%20match%2C%20RR%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20elected%20to%20bowl%20first.%20Almost%20every%20RCB%20batter%20got%20a%20start%2C%20but%20they%20could%20not%20convert%20them%20into%20a%20big%20knock.%20Rajat%20Patidar%20(34%20in%2022%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20(33%20in%2024%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Mahipal%20Lomror%20(32%20in%2017%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20emerged%20as%20top-scorers%2C%20restricting%20RCB%20to%20172%2F8%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAvesh%20Khan%20(3%2F44)%20was%20the%20top%20bowler%20for%20RR.%20Ravichandran%20Ashwin%20(2%2F19)%20and%20Trent%20Boult%20(1%2F16)%20also%20did%20a%20fine%20job%20in%20putting%20brakes%20on%20the%20RCB%20run%20rate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20run-chase%2C%20the%20Royals'%20got%20off%20to%20a%20fine%20start%2C%20with%20Yashasvi%20Jaiswal%20(45%20in%2030%20balls%2C%20with%20eight%20fours)%20and%20Tom%20Kohler%20Cadmore%20(20%20in%2015%20balls%2C%20with%20four%20boundaries)%20putting%20on%20a%2046-run%20stand.%20From%20then%20on%2C%20RCB%20bowlers%20applied%20some%20pressure%20on%20Rajasthan%2C%20restricting%20the%20run-flow%20and%20getting%20some%20wickets.%20RR%20was%20restricted%20to%20112%2F4%20in%2013.1%20overs.%20However%2C%20Riyan%20Parag%20(36%20in%2026%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes)%20held%20one%20end%20before%20he%20was%20dismissed%20while%20Shimron%20Hetmyer%20(26%20in%2014%20balls%2C%20with%20three%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20and%20Rovman%20Powell%20(16*%20in%20eight%20balls%2C%20with%20two%20fours%20and%20a%20six)%20attacked%20RCB%20in%20the%20last%20few%20overs%20to%20get%20a%20four-wicket%20win%20with%20an%20over%20left.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMohammed%20Siraj%20(2%2F33)%20was%20the%20top%20bowler%20for%20RCB.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20took%20home%20the%20'Player%20of%20the%20Match'%20award.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20RR%20will%20meet%20Sunrisers%20Hyderabad%20(SRH)%20in%20qualifier%20two%20on%20May%2024%20in%20Chennai%20to%20decide%20who%20plays%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20(KKR)%20in%20the%20final%20on%20May%2026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716448440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F65uglhp_rcb-kohli-maxwell_625x300_23_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https