r%20long%20bouts%20of%20celibacy.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EShe%20turned%20to%20long-standing%20male%20friends%20for%20romance%20instead%20and%20has%20had%20far%20more%20fun.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202019%2C%20after%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-not-allowed-bring-kids-home-spain-hague-convention-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecoming%20a%20single%20mother%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20only%20alternate%20weekends%20free%20to%20date%2C%20I%20joined%20Tinder%2C%20then%20OK%20Cupid%2C%20and%20even%20spent%20time%20on%20Bumble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20had%20lived%20in%20seven%20countries%2C%20given%20birth%20to%20my%20two%20sons%2C%20and%20gone%20through%20a%20difficult%20breakup%2C%20but%20at%20this%20point%20was%20happily%20settled%20as%20a%20writer%20working%20from%20my%20home%20in%20Spain.%20The%20downside%20was%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsingle-mom-dating-men-without-kids-no-fathers-less-complicated-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emeeting%20men%20in%20real%20life%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20highly%20unlikely.%20I%20decided%20to%20give%20online%20dating%20another%20shot.%20I'd%20done%20it%20circa%202013%2C%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20fun%2C%20and%20found%20both%20long-term%20romances%20and%20friendships.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20since%20then%2C%20the%20apps%20seemed%20to%20have%20changed%20the%20way%20dating%20worked.%20Instead%20of%20spending%20plenty%20of%20time%20on%20dates%2C%20like%20in%20the%20past%2C%20I%20spent%20most%20of%20my%20time%20on%20the%20apps%20having%20boring%20conversations%20that%20led%20nowhere.%20It%20was%20bad%20but%20not%20%E2%80%94%20yet%20%E2%80%94%20quite%20enough%20to%20make%20me%20abandon%20the%20apps%20and%20choose%20celibacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2214463aff-fd6d-4386-ac49-66e2f21e57cf%5C%22%3EI%20was%20cruelly%20ghosted%20by%20an%20app%20hook-up%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20then%2C%20I%20swiped%20on%20a%20truly%20interesting%2C%20attractive%20guy