%22title%22%3A%22'Instead%20Of%20Doli%2C%20She%20Left%20In%20Arthi'%3A%20Mothers%20Mourn%20Porsche%20Victims%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20some%2C%20the%20Pune%20Porsche%20crash%20is%20a%20tragic%20example%20of%20why%20minors%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20drive.%20Many%20see%20it%20as%20a%20test%20of%20the%20country's%20justice%20system.%20For%20another%20section%2C%20the%20question%20is%20whether%20privilege%20will%20again%20enable%20the%20teen%20to%20get%20off%20lightly.%20But%20for%20two%20homes%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20is%20about%20a%20vacuum%20that%20nothing%20can%20ever%20fill.%20For%20them%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Porsche%20case%26quot%3B%20signifies%20endless%20pain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnish%20Awadhiya%20and%20Ashwini%20Kostha%20were%20two%2024-year-old%20engineers%20who%20left%20their%20small%20city%20homes%20with%20many%20dreams.%20That%20night%20in%20Pune%2C%20they%20were%20out%20to%20meet%20friends%20and%20were%20returning%20on%20a%20bike%20when%20a%20drunken%20teen%20at%20the%20wheel%20of%20his%20high-end%20car%20hit%20them%20from%20behind.%20Ashwini%2C%20eyewitnesses%20said%2C%20was%20thrown%2020%20feet%20high%20and%20landed%20hard.%20Aneesh%20was%20thrown%20at%20a%20parked%20car.%20Both%20died%20on%20the%20spot.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20her%20Jabalpur%20home%2C%20Ashwini's%20mother%20Mamata%20is%20still%20in%20shock.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20send%20her%20off%20in%20a%20doli%20(to%20the%20groom's%20house)%20after%20her%20wedding%2C%20but%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20carry%20her%20arthi%20(bier)%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20want%20justice%20for%20Ashwini.%20The%20minor%20boy%20and%20his%20parents%20should%20get%20stringent%20punishment.%20They%20have%20not%20raised%20him%20properly.%20They%20should%20have%20not%20given%20him%20the%20car%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20about%20the%2017-year-old%20driver%2C%20who%20has%20now%20been%20remanded%20in%20an%20observation%20home%20as%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20decides%20whether%20he%20will%20be%20tried%20as%20an%20adult.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPolice%20have%20said%20the%20teenager%20was%20heavily%20drunk%20when%20he%20drove%20the%20Porsche%2C%20reportedly%20at%20200%20km%20per%20hour.%C2%A0The%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20had%20earlier%20granted%20bail%20to%20the%20boy%20on%20conditions%20widely%20considered%20very%20flimsy.%20The%20conditions%20included%20writing%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20%26quot%3Broad%20accident%20and%20their%20solution%26quot%3B%2C%20studying%20traffic%20rules%20for%2015%20days%20and%20attending%20counselling%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit%20and%20psychiatric%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20it%20a%20joke%3F%20What%20essay%20will%20he%20write%3F%20A%20joke%20is%20playing%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Koshta%20said.%20She%20described%20Ashwini%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bvery%20talented%20girl%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BShe%20was%20one%20in%20a%20million.%20She%20had%20so%20many%20dreams%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20tears%20rolling%20down%20her%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwini's%20brother%20Samprit%20told%20NDTV%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Bsmart%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bindependent%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BShe%20excelled%20in%20every%20field.%20She%20had%20plans%20to%20come%20to%20our%20father's%20birthday%20next%20month%20and%20she%20had%20also%20planned%20a%20retirement%20party%20for%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbout%20150%20km%20away%20is%20another%20mother%2C%20whose%20world%20turned%20upside%20down%20that%20night.%20Speaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Savita%20Awadhiya%20held%20herself%20together%20for%20some%20questions%2C%20before%20grief%20won%20and%20she%20could%20not%20hold%20back%20tears%20anymore.%20%26quot%3BHe%20killed%20my%20son.%20Now%2C%20I%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20my%20son.%20It%20is%20the%20boy's%20mistake%2C%20you%20can%20call%20it%20murder.%20If%20he%20had%20not%20made%20such%20a%20big%20mistake%2C%20no%20one%20would%20have%20died.%20If%20only%20his%20family%20members%20had%20paid%20attention%2C%20today%20my%20son%20would%20have%20been%20alive%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Awadhiya%20said%20the%20teen%20driver%20must%20get%20tough%20punishment.%20%26quot%3BHe%20should%20face%20the%20strictest%20punishment.%20They%20are%20trying%20very%20hard%20to%20save%20him.%20They%20are%20people%20with%20money%20and%20think%20can%20save%20their%20son.%20But%20my%20son%20died%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20appealing%20to%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20to%20help%20her%20get%20justice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERemembering%20her%20son%2C%20she%20said%20Aneesh%20wanted%20to%20pursue%20an%20MBA.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20very%20cheerful%2C%20he%20would%20make%20everyone%20his%20own.%20Earlier%20this%20month%2C%20he%20came%20home%20for%20an%20anniversary.%20He%20was%20planning%20to%20visit%20again%20soon.%20He%20had%20told%20me%20he%20was%20getting%20me%20a%20gift%20for%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnish's%20father%20Om%20Awadhiya%20said%20he%20was%20a%20responsible%20son%20who%20shouldered%20family%20responsibilities.%20His%20younger%20brother%20was%20staying%20with%20him%20in%20Pune%20and%20he%20took%20care%20of%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20culprit%20will%20get%20punishment...%20But%20how%20can%20we%20bring%20back%20our%20child%20now%3F%20He%20spoke%20to%20his%20mother%20two%20days%20before%20the%20accident%20and%20told%20us%20he%20will%20come%20soon.%20He%20was%20a%20big%20support%20for%20the%20family.%20What%20will%20happen%20to%20my%20younger%20son%20now%3F%20Who%20will%20take%20care%20of%20him%20in%20Pune%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1716446400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2F9nhnpmn_ashwini-pune-650-_625x300_23_May_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-ashwini-kostha-anish-awadhiya-instead-of-doli-she-left-in-arthi-mothers-mourn-porsche-victims-5726529%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20two%20homes%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20it%20is%20about%20a%20vacuum%20that%20nothing%20can%20ever%20fill.%20For%20them%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20Porsche%20case%26quot%3B%20signifies%20endless%20pain.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-ashwini-kostha-anish-awadhiya-instead-of-doli-she-left-in-arthi-mothers-mourn-porsche-victims-5726529%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-ashwini-kostha-anish-awadhiya-instead-of-doli-she-left-in-arthi-mothers-mourn-porsche-victims-5726529%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fpune-porsche-crash-ashwini-kostha-anish-awadhiya-instead-of-doli-she-left-in-arthi-mothers-mourn-porsche-victims-5726529%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Nurse%20Who%20Killed%20Baby%20By%20Strapping%20Face%20To%20Bean%20Bag%20Jailed%20For%2014%20Years%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20nursery%20nurse%20who%20killed%20a%20baby%20by%20strapping%20her%20face%20down%20to%20a%20bean%20bag%20has%20been%20sentenced%20to%2014%20years%20in%20prison%2C%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.independent.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fuk%2Fcrime%2Fgenevieve-meehan-death-nursery-worker-b2549460.html%5C%22%3EIndependent%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported.%C2%A0%20The%20court%20heard%20how%20Kate%20Roughley%20strapped%20nine-month-old%20Genevieve%20Meehan%20face%20down%20onto%20a%20bean%20bag%20for%20more%20than%2090%20minutes%20as%20a%20punishment%20for%20not%20sleeping%20for%20long%20enough.%20The%20nurse%C2%A0then%20tightly%20swaddled%20her%20before%20she%20further%20restrained%20her%20with%20a%20harness%20and%20then%20inappropriately%20covered%20her%20with%20a%20blanket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20baby%20ultimately%20suffocated%20to%20death%20at%20Tiny%20Toes%20Nursery%20in%20Cheadle%20Hulme%2C%20Stockport%2C%20on%20May%209%202022.%C2%A0Despite%20paramedics'%20efforts%20to%20save%20her%2C%20she%20was%20pronounced%20dead%20later%20that%20day%20in%20hospital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20jury%20unanimously%20found%20Roughley%20guilty%20of%20manslaughter%20by%20ill-treatment%20this%20week%20following%20a%20four-week%20trial%20at%20Manchester%20Crown%20Court.%C2%A0%20Jurors%20were%20in%20tears%20when%20they%20watched%20nursery%20CCTV%20footage%20of%20the%20baby%20room%2C%20which%20captured%20the%20tragedy%20unfolding.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FJAILED%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23JAILED%3C%2Fa%3E%20%7C%20Nursery%20worker%20jailed%20for%20the%20manslaughter%20of%209-month-old%20baby%20Genevieve.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnKate%20Roughley%20(04%2F03%2F1987)%20has%20been%20jailed%20for%2014%20years.%20She%20was%20found%20guilty%20of%20manslaughter%20following%20a%20four-week%20trial.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnRead%20more%20about%20our%20investigation%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FvieNLOTIRO%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FvieNLOTIRO%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2Fpoodj6KFu1%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2Fpoodj6KFu1%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Greater%20Manchester%20Police%20(%40gmpolice)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fgmpolice%2Fstatus%2F1793296771155689949%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProsecutor%20Peter%20Wright%20KC%20said%20the%20baby's%20desperate%20fight%20for%20survival%20was%20clear%20but%20her%20crying%20and%20the%20thrashing%20and%20writhing%20of%20her%20body%20were%20routinely%20and%20repeatedly%20ignored.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMrs%20Justice%20Ellenbogen%20told%20Roughley%20that%20Genevieve's%20death%20was%20%26quot%3Babsolutely%20avoidable%26quot%3B%20and%C2%A0that%20she%20had%20%26quot%3Bno%20genuine%20remorse%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20baby's%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Ellenbogen%20further%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BAs%20the%20harrowing%20CCTV%20audio%20and%20video%20footage%20showed%2C%20that%20day%20you%20left%20Genevieve%20in%20that%20position%20only%20carrying%20the%20most%20cursory%20and%20infrequent%20of%20checks.%20I%20am%20certain%20that%20every%20person%20in%20this%20courtroom%20who%20watched%20that%20footage%20was%20willing%20you%20to%20pick%20her%20up%20and%20remove%20her%20from%20the%20danger%20you%20had%20placed%20her%2C%20knowing%20of%20course%20that%20you%20didn't.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20continued%3A%20%26quot%3BYou%20berated%20her%20for%20only%20sleeping%20for%2020%20minutes%20having%20called%20her%20vile.%20She%20was%20placed%20on%20a%20beanbag...%20notwithstanding%20her%20kicking%20wriggling%2C%20arching%20of%20her%20back%20and%20tears%20you%20left%20her%20there.%20Her%20crying%20intensified%2C%20and%20acquired%20a%20grunting%20tone...%20even%20then%20you%20didn't%20approach%20her%2C%20pick%20her%20up%2C%20or%20show%20concern%20for%20her%20welfare.%20You%20left%20her%20to%20die.%20Your%20interactions%20palpably%20lacked%20any%20care%2C%20kindness%20or%20concern%20for%20her%20wellbeing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInspector%20Charlotte%20Whalley%2C%20the%20senior%20investigating%20officer%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BThis%20has%20been%20a%20truly%20harrowing%20and%20disturbing%20investigation.%20The%20impact%20of%20Roughley's%20abhorrent%20crime%20is%20immense%20and%20far-reaching.%20Genevieve's%20life%20was%20robbed%2C%20and%20others%20must%20now%20live%20with%20the%20painful%20consequences%20of%20Roughley's%20actions.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20defendant's%20case%20was%20that%20Genevieve's%20death%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bterrible%20and%20unavoidable%20accident%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20the%20result%20of%20any%20unlawful%20acts.%3C%2Fp