0whether%20he%20will%20be%20tried%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20and%20his%20father%20in%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20hours%20after%20the%20chilling%20accident%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20had%20granted%20bail%20to%20the%20teen%2C%20who%20was%20caught%20drinking%20on%20camera%20shortly%20before%20he%20drove%20the%20high-end%20car%20at%20over%20240%20km%20per%20hour%2C%20with%20a%20set%20of%20conditions.%20The%20conditions%20included%20writing%20a%20300-word%20essay%20on%20%26quot%3Broad%20accident%20and%20their%20solution%26quot%3B%2C%20studying%20traffic%20rules%20for%2015%20days%20and%20attending%20counselling%20for%20his%20drinking%20habit%20and%20psychiatric%20treatment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENews%20of%20the%20bail%20and%20its%20conditions%20sparked%20massive%20outrage%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20many%20alleging%20that%20the%20teenager%2C%20son%20of%20a%20prominent%20Pune%20realtor%2C%20had%20been%20let%20off%20very%20lightly%20for%20a%20heinous%20crime%20that%20led%20to%20two%20untimely%20deaths.%20Pune%20police%20said%20they%20had%20urged%20the%20board%20for%20permission%20to%20try%20the%20accused%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20but%20it%20refused.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20growing%20outrage%2C%20police%20on%20Monday%20registered%20a%20case%20against%20the%20teen's%20father%20under%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Act.%20A%20case%20was%20also%20registered%20against%20the%20owners%20and%20staff%20of%20two%20bars%20that%20served%20alcohol%20to%20the%2017-year-old%20and%20his%20two%20friends.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20the%20realtor%20father%20was%20arrested%20after%20GPS%20tracking%20foiled%20his%20elaborate%20escape%20plan%20that%20involved%20multiple%20vehicles.%20The%20bar%20owners%20and%20staff%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%20too.%20In%20a%20surprise%20visit%2C%20Maharashtra%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20reached%20Pune%20to%20review%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20Pune%20police's%20review%20petition%2C%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20the%20teenaged%20accused.%20During%20the%20hearing%2C%20the%20board%20modified%20its%20earlier%20order%2C%20remanding%20the%20accused%20in%20an%20observation%20home%20till%20June%205.%20On%20police's%20plea%20for%20permission%20to%20try%20him%20as%20an%20adult%2C%20the%20board%20has%20sought%20a%20reply%20from%20the%20defendant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Pune%20Police%20Commissioner%20Amitesh%20Kumar%20said%20they%20moved%20two%20applications%20with%20the%20court%20on%20Sunday.%20%26quot%3BOne%20was%20this%20that%20is%20a%20heinous%20crime%20and%20the%20accused%20must%20be%20tried%20as%20an%20adult.%20Our%20second%20application%20was%20that%20till%20the%20time%20this%20is%20decided%2C%20the%20accused%20must%20be%20at%20an%20observation%20home.%20These%20applications%20were%20disallowed%20that%20day.%20So%20we%20sought%20a%20review%2C%20we%20have%20got%20a%20favourable%20order%20on%20both%20counts%20today%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20top%20cop%20said%20the%20accused's%20blood%20test%20reports%2C%20which%20are%20yet%20to%20come%20in%2C%20are%20%26quot%3Bnot%20very%20important%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThis%20case%20is%20not%20about%20an%20accident%20in%20which%20a%20mistake%20happened%20under%20the%20influence%20of%20alcohol%20and%20people%20died.%20Our%20case%20is%20that%20he%20had%20full%20knowledge%20that%20his%20conduct...%20he%20parties%20in%20two%20bars%2C%20rashly%20drives%20a%20car%20without%20a%20number%20plate%20on%20a%20narrow%2C%20congested%20street.%20He%20was%20fully%20in%20his%20senses%20and%20he%20knew%20that%20people%20may%20die%20because%20of%20his%20actions.%20Our%20case%20is%20under%20Section%20304%20of%20IPC%20which%20carries%20a%20jail%20term%20of%2010%20years.%20And%20this%20is%20not%20our%20stand%20after%20the%20media%20outrage%2C%20this%20is%20our%20stand%20since%20Sunday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kumar%20said%20the%20accused's%20counsel%20has%20been%20asked%20to%20respond%20by%20tomorrow%20to%20the%20police%20plea%20of%20trying%20him%20as%20an%20adult.%20%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20we%20will%20get%20the%20permission%20to%20try%20him%20as%20an%20adult%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused's%20lawyer%2C%20Prashant%20Patil%2C%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20teenager%20will%20be%20at%20a%20rehabilitation%20home%20till%20June%205.%20%26quot%3BDuring%20this%20time%2C%20he%20will%20undergo%20counselling%20and%20other%20steps%20will%20be%20taken%20to%20bring%20him%20to%20the%20mainstream%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Madhya%20Pradesh%2C%20over%20a%20thousand%20kilometres%20away%2C%20the%20families%20of%20Ashwini%20Koshtha%20and%20Aneesh%20Awadhiya%2C%20who%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20accident%2C%20are%20living%20through%20their%20worst%20nightmare.%20The%20families%20have%20termed%20this%20%26quot%3Bmurder%26quot%3B%20and%20not%20an%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20NDTV%2C%20Aneesh's%20mother%20Savita%20Awadhiya%20broke%20down%20last%20night.%20%26quot%3BHe%20killed%20my%20son.%20Now%2C%20I%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20meet%20my%20son%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20the%20boy's%20mistake%2C%20you%20can%20call%20it%20murder%2C%20because%20if%20he%20had%20not%20made%20such%20a%20big%20mistake%2C%20no%20one%20would%20have%20died.%20If%20only%20his%20family%20members%20had%20paid%20attention%2C%20today%20my%20son%20would%20have%20been%20alive.%20This%20is%20murder%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwini%20Koshta's%20mother%20Mamata%20Koshta%20told%20news%20agency%20PTI%20that%20she%20was%20very%20talented%20and%20had%20so%20many%20dreams.%20%26quot%3BWe%20were%20supposed%20to%20send%20her%20off%20in%20a%20palanquin%20(to%20the%20groom's%20house)%20after%20her%20marriage.%20Now%20we%20are%20forced%20to%20carry%20her%20body%20on%20a%20bier%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%