ip%20and%20engineering%20roles%20in%20PayPal%20and%20Facebook%2C%20per%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fyishan-wong%2Fdetails%2Fexperience%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20profile%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Carnegie%20Mellon%20University%20graduate%20was%20Reddit's%20CEO%20for%20nearly%20two%20years%20before%20leaving%20the%20social%20network%20in%202014.%20Wong%20is%20currently%20the%20CEO%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fterraformation-ex-reddit-ceo-raises-30-million-tree-planting-startup-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ETerraformation%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20climate%20change-focused%20and%20forest%20restoration%20startup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20this%20means%20is%20that%20now%20we're%20getting%20shittier%20products%20because%20the%20tech%20giants%20are%20obsessed%20with%20'competing%20on%20AI'%20instead%20of%20just%20delivering%20good%20and%20useful%20products%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20said%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fplatform.twitter.com%2Fwidgets.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20big%20internet%20giants%20are%20in%20a%20state%20of%20memetic%20competition%20over%20AI%2C%20with%20Google's%20existential%20fear%20of%20OpenAI%20in%20the%20center%20ring.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThis%20is%20leading%20to%20all%20of%20them%20integrating%20LLM-powered%20AI%20into%20their%20products%2C%20but%20the%20AI%20sometimes%20gives%20flawed%20answers%2C%20which%20is%20problematic%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%E2%80%94%20Yishan%20(%40yishan)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fyishan%2Fstatus%2F1793411768255238410%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EMay%2022%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fact%20that%20tech%20products%20can%20be%20rolled%20out%20and%20distributed%20quickly%20has%20made%20the%20drop%20in%20quality%20even%20more%20pronounced%2C%20Wong%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20makes%20the%20current%20situation%20shitty%20is%20that%20the%20giants%20force%20everyone%20to%20use%20the%20LLM-powered%20products%20because%20they%20are%20cloud-based%2C%26quot%3B%20Wong%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fyishan%2Fstatus%2F1793422918845931827%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20an%20X%20user%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2FBotTachikoma%2Fstatus%2F1793415121928348048%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elikened%20today's%20AI%20products%20to%20the%20cars%20that%20were%20first%20invented%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20cars%2C%20people%20could%20still%20keep%20using%20horses.%20It%20wasn't%20a%20wholesale%20product%20changeover%20-%20people%20adopted%20as%20the%20product%20improved%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWong's%20former%20company%20Reddit%20does%20seem%20eager%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20AI%20revolution.%20In%20February%2C%20the%20social%20media%20platform%20said%20Google%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-train-ai-model-crazy-subreddit-posts-reddit-licensing-deal-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elicensing%20its%20content%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20train%20their%20AI%20models.%20Reddit%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-openai-deal-ai-data-partnership-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruck%20a%20similar%20deal%20with%20OpenAI%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20month%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Wong%20didn't%20immediately%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment%20from%20BI%20sent%20outside%20regular%20business%20hours.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWong's%20comments%20echo%20that%20of%20former%20Google%20employee%2C%20Scott%20Jenson.%20On%20Monday%2C%20Jenson%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessi