mp-standard-jury-charge-falsifying-business-records-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estandard%20charging%20language%3C%2Fa%3E%20barely%20fills%20two%20pages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20for%20each%20count%2C%20the%20jury%20must%20consider%20just%20two%20things%3A%20whether%20Trump%20caused%20the%20record%20to%20be%20falsified%2C%20and%20whether%20he%20did%20so%20to%20hide%20his%20intent%20to%20commit%20%26quot%3Banother%20crime.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20prosecutors%20meet%20their%20burden%20to%20prove%20both%20tiers%20%E2%80%94%20falsification%20and%20intent%20to%20conceal%20another%20crime%20%E2%80%94%20beyond%20a%20reasonable%20doubt%2C%20then%20Trump%20is%20guilty.%20If%20they%20don't%2C%20then%20Trump%20is%20not%20guilty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20don't%20even%20have%20to%20prove%20that%20%26quot%3Banother%20crime%26quot%3B%20was%20actually%20committed.%20They%20just%20have%20to%20prove%20that%20Trump%20intended%20to%20commit%20another%20crime%20and%20then%20falsified%20records%20to%20hide%20his%20tracks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20charge%20for%20this%20single%20felony%20should%20be%20easy%2C%20right%3F%20Clear-cut%20and%20beyond%20dispute%3F%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYes%2C%20first-degree%20falsifying%20is%20the%20only%20law%20in%20Trump's%20indictment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20law%20jurors%20must%20understand%20and%20weigh%20when%20they%20begin%20deliberations%20as%20early%20as%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20allege%20that%20Trump%20falsified%20the%20hush-money%20reimbursements%20in%20order%20to%20conceal%20his%20intent%20to%20commit%20an%20obscure%20New%20York%20election-conspiracy%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20what%20they%20mean%20by%20Trump's%20%26quot%3Bintent%20to%20commit%20another%20crime.%26quot%3B%20Under%20the%20prosecution%20theory%2C%20this%20%26quot%3Banother%20crime%26quot%3B%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-hush-money-case-relies-never-used-election-conspiracy-law-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eelection%20law%20section%2017-152%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20it%20makes%20it%20a%20misdemeanor%20to%20conspire%20to%20influence%20an%20election%20%26quot%3Bby%20unlawful%20means.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Section%2017-152%20of%20the%20New%20York%20state%20election%20law.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662c4ec523b29110d303df20%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221438%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EManhattan%20prosecutors%20say%20violating%20this%20state%20election%20law%20makes%20Donald%20Trump%20a%20felon.%3Cp%3ENY%20State%20Election%20Law%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229b1bcaff-9b45-454a-9a2f-bd8330e8e51e%5C%22%3EA%20crime%20within%20a%20crime%20within%20a%20crime%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20you%20see%2C%20to%20win%20a%20conviction%2C%20prosecutors%20must%20demonstrate%20three%20layers%20of%20unlawfulness%20involving%20at%20least%20three%20separate%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey're%20alleging%20Trump%20committed%20a%20crime%20(under%20the%20Federal%20Elections%20Campaign%20Act)%20within%20a%20crime%20(under%20the%20state%20election-conspiracy%20law)%20within%20a%20crime%20(under%20the%20first-degree%20falsifying%20charge%20he's%20actually%20indicted%20on).%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20Russian%20nesting%20doll%20of%20wrongdoing%2C%20though%20only%20the%20outermost%20doll%2C%20first-degree%20falsifying%2C%20needs%20to%20be%20proven%20beyond%20a%20reasonable%20doubt.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EProsecutors%20also%20plan%20to%20give%20jurors%20two%20alternatives%20to%20the%20FECA%20violation%2C%20that%20innermost%20of%20the%20three%20nesting%20dolls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20alternatives%20are%20a%20violation%20of%20federal%2C%20state%2C%20and%2For%20city%20tax%20laws%20(alleging%20that%20Cohen's%20hush-money%20reimbursements%20were%20unlawfully%20disguised%20as%20taxable%20income)%20and%20yet%20another%20records-falsification%20violation%20(alleging%20that%20Trump%20was%20responsible%20for%20bogus%20hush-money%20paperwork%20at%20the%20National%20Enquirer.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20three%20layers%20of%20wrongdoing%20under%20a%20half-dozen%20potentially%20applicable%20laws%2C%20all%20with%20their%20own%20wording%20and%20definitions%2C%20much%20of%20which%20had%20to%20be%20argued%20over%20on%20Tuesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bconspiracy%3F%26quot%3B%20What%20is%20%26quot%3Bintent%3F%26quot%3B%20What%20is%20%26quot%3Baccessorial%20liability%3F%26quot%3B%20Do%20those%20definitions%20differ%2C%20law%20to%20law%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20were%20broader%2C%20more%20arcane%20questions%2C%20including%20this%20one%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMust%20jurors%20agree%20unanimously%20on%20the%20%26quot%3Bunlawful%20means%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20case%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeaning%2C%20must%20all%2012%20jurors%20agree%20that%2C%20in%20causing%20Cohen%20to%20pay%20the%20hush%20money%2C%20Trump%20conspired%20to%20violate%20FECA%20campaign-contribution%20limits%3F%20Or%20can%20some%20jurors%20find%20that%20Trump%20conspired%20to%20violate%20tax%20law%2C%20while%20other%20jurors%20see%20the%20falsification%20of%20National%20Enquirer%20business%20records%20as%20the%20central%20offense%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20other%20words%2C%20do%20jurors%20need%20to%20be%20unanimous%20in%20deciding%20which%20of%20the%20three%20options%2C%20if%20any%2C%20is%20the%20central%20unlawfulness%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20brings%20us%20back%20to%20Tuesday's%20charge%20conference%20and%20why%20the%20sides%20fought%20for%20three%20hours%20as%20the%20defendant%2C%20and%20many%20in%20the%20audience%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-nap-trial-affect-jury-legal-experts-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estruggled%20to%20stay%20awake%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%2C%20obviously%2C%20an%20extraordinari