ods%20weren%E2%80%99t%20being%20kind.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20he%20persisted%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Ganesh%2C%20adding%20that%20the%201%2C000%20trees%20flourished.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20joined%20my%20father%20in%20farming%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F347565%2Fgrow-mangoes-chikoo-fruits-on-trees-urban-gardener-jayanti-sahoo-terrace-gardening-tips%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplant%20another%201%2C000%20mango%20saplings%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20today%2C%20we%20have%20over%202%2C000%20mango%20trees.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENaturally%2C%20the%20farm%20always%20had%20an%20audience.%20People%20were%20intrigued%20at%20how%20the%20father-son%20duo%20had%20created%20a%20yellow%20oasis%2C%20and%20the%20organic%20methods%20they%20had%20used%20to%20achieve%20the%20feat.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20many%20guests%20who%20wanted%20to%20observe%20how%20we%20were%20preparing%20our%20organic%20fertilisers%20from%20cow%20dung%20(we%20had%2035%20cows%20in%20our%20shed)%2C%20how%20we%20used%20neem%20to%20make%20our%20pesticides%2C%20and%20how%20our%20mangoes%20were%20thriving%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ganesh%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Ganesh%20Agro%20Tourism%20homestay%20lies%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20Ratnagiri%20and%20Sindhudurg%20districts%20of%20Maharashtra%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F05%2Fmango-homestay-5-1715946632-500x262.j