f%20Flowers!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%3F%C2%A0%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImagine%20this%20%E2%80%94%20you%20are%20surrounded%20by%20lush%20green%20mountains%20with%20crystal%20clear%20streams%20of%20water%20running%20through%20them.%20Sounds%20straight%20out%20of%20a%20storybook%2C%20right%3F%20The%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%2C%20a%20UNESCO-protected%20site%20will%20surpass%20all%20your%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%20was%20discovered%20by%20the%20British%20mountaineer%20and%20botanist%20Frank%20Smythe.%20In%201931%2C%20Smythe%20and%20his%20climbing%20partner%20R%20L%20Holdsworth%20stumbled%20upon%20the%20valley%20while%20returning%20from%20a%20successful%20expedition%20to%20Mount%20Kamet.%20Enchanted%20by%20the%20natural%20beauty%20of%20the%20area%2C%20Smythe%20wrote%20about%20his%20experience%20in%20his%20book%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F36699%2Fvalley-of-flowers-trek-route%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Valley%20of%20Flowers%E2%80%9D%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20published%20in%201937.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAptly%20put%20by%20an%3Cem%3E%20Inside%20Himalayas%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20don%E2%80%99t%20quite%20understand%20how%20lucky%20you%20are%20until%20you%20get%20there.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhatever%20you%20might%20have%20heard%2C%20whatever%20photographs%20you%20might%20have%20seen%2C%20absolutely%20nothing%20prepares%20you%20for%20that%20burst%20of%20colour%20as%20far%20as%20the%20eyes%20can%20see%2C%20framed%20by%20mist-shrouded%2C%20snow-powdered%20mountain%20ranges%20whose%20tops%20disappear%20into%20the%20sky.%20You%20feel%20as%20though%20you%20have%20arrived%20at%20the%20top%20of%20the%20world%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20article%20elaborates.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%2